# Used when building / deploying the frontend (e.g. Vercel).
# Public HTTPS URL of your Agent Olympics API — no trailing slash.
# Example: https://agent-olympics-api.up.railway.app
#
# When set:
# - Leaderboard + SSE talk to this URL
# - “Backend URL” on /arena.html is pre-filled for tokens + CLI --backend
#
# Leave unset for local dev (Vite proxies /api → http://localhost:3001)

VITE_API_URL=
